<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Install" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Install,</orth> to place in a rank or office, to instate: <cit><quote>--ed me in the diadem,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 2.5.89" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A II, 5, 89</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>--ed in that high degree,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.1.17" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 17</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>is my lord of Winchester --ed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.1.28" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 28</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.1.46" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 1, 46</bibl>. <cit><quote>Cranmer is --ed lord archbishop,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.402" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 402</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>